    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That recover function will accurately recover signers, but will not ensure that the signature is canonical and consensus acceptable.\r\n\r\nYou need to invoke [`signature.normalize_s()`](https://docs.rs/ecdsa/0.16.6/ecdsa/struct.Signature.html#method.normalize_s) and check the result of the operation is `None`\r\n\r\nAdding this should remediate:\r\n```\r\nif  s.normalize_s().is_some() {\r\n    return Err(Signature::RecoveryError);\r\n}\r\n```",
